metadata.description:
To celebrate our first anniversary, we’re dropping a mixtape and airdropping one edition to all current Sound collectors.

The mix includes 53 songs submitted by artists in our community, which comprises just a fraction of the incredible music on Sound but represents the diverse genres and remarkable talent on Sound.

Sound would not exist without the continued support of our community of artists and collectors. Thank you for building alongside us – we’re excited to keep you updated on what we have in store for the next year.
